# Axodus Portfolio Roadmap

Last refreshed: 2026-06-30

## Current Portfolio Sequence

1. `DOCUMENTATION-EPIC-01 - Publication Authority and Versioning Consolidation` — next best move; governance/documentation consolidation only, with no publication or production authority implied.
2. `BBA-AGENCY-EPIC-01 - BBA-Agency L4 Candidate Advancement` — alternate bounded local/non-production track.
3. `DEFI-REMEDIATION-EPIC-01 - Defi Security Surface and Execution Boundary Remediation` — alternate remediation-only track; no feature implementation or financial authority.

Current holds:

- Marketplace Phase 12A remains `HOLD / BACKLOG_READY`, not immediate priority.
- Academy EPIC-02 and Mining EPIC-02 are not automatic follow-ons.
- ACS remains paused; do not open `ACS-GOV-03` or `ACS-GOV-04`.
- Trading and Lottery execution work remains blocked.
- Defi feature implementation remains blocked until remediation is completed and separately reviewed.

This roadmap sequence does not open production, financial, treasury, custody, execution, wallet/signing, settlement, payout, billing, provider or contract-write gates. Older roadmap sections are historical planning records.

Last updated: 2026-06-23

