## 2026-06-08 - Portfolio Gated Advancement Review

Status: COMPLETE

Portfolio recommendation: PORTFOLIO_READY_FOR_SELECTIVE_L4_ADVANCEMENT

Selected next cycle: Business L4 Consolidation

Rationale:

- Trading revalidation passed and Trading is L4 candidate.
- ACS gate review passed and ACS is L4 candidate.
- Business, Mining, Academy and Marketplace were promoted to L4 candidate during the validation refresh.
- Documentation and Dex are L4 readiness tracks with publication/execution boundaries preserved.
- Core and Governance remain high-confidence L5 contractual nuclei, but not production/runtime expansion targets.

Next cycle:

1. Business L4 Consolidation.
2. Preserve billing, payment, treasury, ACS provisioning and governance execution as blocked.
3. Produce stronger persistence, repository contract, billing boundary and integration readiness evidence.
4. Do not start production billing, payment, treasury or customer execution.

Deferred cycles:

- Marketplace L4 Consolidation: deferred due to payment/settlement/value-transfer risk.
- Academy L4 Consolidation: deferred due to reward, certification, contract deployment and treasury risk.
- Mining L4 Consolidation: deferred until provider/payout warnings and custody boundaries are hardened.
- Dex L4 Consolidation: paused after DEX-REQ-11 by executive directive.
- AxodusAPP Integration Expansion: deferred until at least one domain nucleus completes bounded L4 consolidation.
- Cross-Nucleus Integration Cycle: deferred until Business L4 consolidation produces stable contracts.
- Defi Phase 3 Planning: remains planning-only and requires separate governance/custody decision.

No roadmap item authorizes production readiness, live trading, swaps, wallet signing, treasury movement, payment/payout/settlement execution, minting, production credentials or on-chain writes.

Current baseline: RECAST 01 - Nucleus Maturity Audit & Baseline Register.

Current allocation: PORTFOLIO SPRINT 01 - Balanced Roadmap & Sprint Allocation.

## Near-Term Portfolio Order

1. PORTFOLIO SPRINT 01 - Balanced Roadmap & Sprint Allocation.
2. PORTFOLIO SPRINT 02 - Lowest-Level Nucleus Recovery.
3. PORTFOLIO SPRINT 03 - Second Lowest-Level Nucleus Recovery.
4. PORTFOLIO SPRINT 04 - Cross-Nucleus AxodusAPP Visibility Planning.

